gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

After consenting with patience, I believe that to be the truth;
Many people have praised the society, but none have remembered any matter.

Here is the translation:

"May it be auspicious time, Lord's will be done; 
May there be sweet sounds of merriment without bounds."

Here is the translation:

Make three o'clock evening prayer, take five grasses and eat food;
Do not do anything on this day, keep love in Guru's service.

Here is the translation:

Going with begging alms to Guru's place, I got emotional longing; 
After that, I went to Kashi only for my livelihood, Guru made me settle in society.

Here is the translation:

Yellow turban on head, a gentle and beautiful cane;
One who has gone mad with devotion, has made himself ready to learn, wondering how he can prepare.

Here is the translation:

Those who came with their own identity, sat among Brahmins as Ghanshyam; 
The Lord sat where the twice-born people are, and He shines very much like Dharniraj.
